<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="sec-cofactors-of-a-matrix"
    xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Cofactors of a Matrix</title>
    <introduction xml:id="subsec-cofactors-of-a-matrix">
        <p>
            <idx>
                <h>Matrices</h>
                <h>Cofactors</h>
            </idx>
            The cofactor <m>c_{ij}</m> is computed as <m>c_{ij} = (-1)^{i+j} M_{ij}</m>, where <m>M_{ij}</m>
            is the minor obtained by deleting the <m>i</m>-th row and <m>j</m>-th column of <m>A</m>.
        </p>
        <sage>
            <input>
                A = matrix([[1, 2, 3], [5, 7, 11], [13, 17, 19]])

                # By Removing first row and second column
                minor_1_2 = det(A.delete_rows([0]).delete_columns([1]))

                # Cofactor c_12
                cofactor_1_2=(-1)^(1+2) * minor_1_2
                print("c_12:", cofactor_1_2)
            </input>
        </sage>
    </introduction>
</section>
